      </p>
      <div class="section1">
        <h5>How To Use 'Bubble n Squeak</h5>
        <p>
          You can view recipes by clicking the recipe link then selecting
          filters to find the right recipe suited for you.
        </p>
        <p>
          To create recipes, you need to create an account. Just click on the
          avatar icon to register.
        </p>
        <p><i>Guide to our recipe list</i></p>
