      <p style="padding-top:1.5%;"><i>Guide to viewing a recipe</i></p>
       
      <figure>
        <img src="/images/recipeViewLuie.png" alt="screenshot of recipe view page" style="width: 100%;" class="img-thumbnail">
        <figcaption style="text-align: center;">
          <ul>
            <li>The recipe name and description appear at the top of the page</li>
            <li>The recipe author appears below the description</li>
            <li>The number of upvotes the recipe has received appears at the bottom of the page</li>
            <li>If included in the recipe, a link to the recipe inspiration appears below upvotes</li>
            <li>If the recipe is scrambled, a link to the original recipe is also included</li>
            <li>Press 'Report' to notify a moderator of an issue with the recipe. You may only report each recipe once</li>
            <li>Press 'Upvote' to like a recipe and save it to your account page. Press again to remove your upvote</li>
            <li>Press the notepad to scramble the recipe</li>
            <li>SCRAMBLING ALLOWS YOU TO CREATE YOUR OWN VERSION OF A PRE-EXISTING RECIPE!!!</li>
          </ul>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
        
        <p style="padding-top:1.5%;"><i>Guide to creating a recipe</i></p>
       
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/recipeCreation.jpeg" alt="screenshot of recipe creation page" style="width: 100%;" class="img-thumbnail">
          <figcaption style="text-align: center;">
            <ul>
              <li>Fill the form and enter each ingredient you will need</li>
              <li>Press add when you want to add another ingredient</li>
              <li>Delete an ingredient by pressing the bin icon</li>

            </ul>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>

      
      <br>
      
      
        <p style="border-top: 5px dotted #ec8e22; padding-top: 1.5%;"><i>Your Account - needed to create recipes</i></p>
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/accountPage.png" alt="screenshot of recipe creation page" style="width: 100%;" class="img-thumbnail">
          <figcaption style="text-align: center;">
            <ul>
              <li>Your username and email are displayed at the top of the page</li>
              <li>Pressing 'Change Password' produces a drop down where you can enter your old password and new password</li>
              <li>Press confirm in the drop down to update your password</li>
              <li>Any recipes you have upvoted will appear in the 'Your Upvoted Recipes' section</li>
              <li>Any recipes you have created will appear in the 'Your Recipes' section</li>
              <li>Press the notebook to edit one of your created recipes</li>
              <li>Press the bin to delete one of your created recipes</li>
              <li>Press the pen to create a new recipe</li>
            </ul>
          </figcaption>
